Package org.hibernate.internal.log

Interface UrlMessageBundle

  • @MessageLogger(projectCode="HHH")
@ValidIdRange(min=10000001,
              max=10001000)
public interface UrlMessageBundle
    Acts as the MessageLogger and MessageBundle for messages related to processing URLs.

void logUnableToFindFileByUrl​(URL url,

                              Exception e)

        Parameters:
